Some exciting new features:
- The classified search function of conversation chat records has come, which supports searching according to text, pictures, documents and other formats to improve work efficiency.
- The calendar function gets a new upgrade: a new UI interface, adding repetitive calendar settings, attachment upload, rejection status viewing and source message jumping functions; and support one-click to quickly create group chat for discussion;
- New collaborative document function is added in the session to improve team collaboration efficiency.
- New unread @ message boot is added to the session to locate important messages quickly.
- Supporting quick response in lock screen notification and notification bar to improve work efficiency;

Some functional optimizations to enhance user experience:
- VOIP voice-conference supports sharing invitations to sessions and gathering participants quickly.
- Provides a mode of using columns on the iPad device;
- Adding a text size choice to enhance the reading experience;

Some experience upgrades for international users:
- Users from different tenants can now communicate with each other to improve the efficiency of cross-country collaboration.
- The promotion of agenda, tasks and upgrade reminders supports English and optimizes the reading experience.

